features: 【Adorable Pop of Color 】 Charming rabbit & carrot pattern printed decorative pillow without inserts. The cute watercolor easter holiday elements which give the indoor home and outdoor porch a modern farmhouse look.

【No Pillow Insert or Filler Included】 A set of 2 easter throw pillow covers in beige. Without any pillow inserts or fillers. Use soft inserts and they will become the designated napping pillow for the household.

【Quality Fabric】 Made of durable polyester & linen blended fabric, it feels like a soft burlap to the touch and won't hurt your skin. It is more suitable for decoration than as bedding. No colour fading, No bad smell.

【Invisible Zipper】 Set of 2 spring throw pillow covers 18 x 18 inch, simple and warm. The zipper at the bottom of the vintage pillow cover is convenient for stuffing the pillow insert while not affecting the aesthetics.

【Good Workmanship】The polyester fabric is reinforced with stitched edges on the inside and at the end of the zipper. However, since the fabric is hand cut, please allow 0.2-0.5 inches of size error. It does not affect normal use.
